@SenderHost = http://localhost:5200

### Health check
GET {{SenderHost}}/health
Accept: application/json

### Send weather request (Sender → Receiver → Sender → JSON)
GET {{SenderHost}}/api/send-weather?city=Amsterdam&days=3&includeHourly=true
Accept: application/json

### Send notification (Sender → Receiver → ACK)
POST {{SenderHost}}/api/send-notification
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "source": "HttpFile",
  "text": "Hello from .http test",
  "level": "Info",
  "tags": ["test", "demo"]
}
